{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016KDingE8xsaY4bCC5DFkde","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→import type { UIMatch } from \"../types\";\n     2→import { TIER_COLORS } from \"@rng-utopia/ui\";\n     3→import { PlayerAvatar, getDisplayName } from \"../../player-profile\";\n     4→\n     5→interface MatchCardProps {\n     6→  match: UIMatch;\n     7→  onJoin?: () => void;\n     8→  isOwn?: boolean;\n     9→  canJoin?: boolean;\n    10→  joining?: boolean;\n    11→}\n    12→\n    13→export function MatchCard({\n    14→  match,\n    15→  onJoin,\n    16→  isOwn = false,\n    17→  canJoin = true,\n    18→  joining = false,\n    19→}: MatchCardProps) {\n    20→  const timeAgo = getTimeAgo(match.createdAt);\n    21→\n    22→  return (\n    23→    <div className={`coinflip-match-card ${isOwn ? \"coinflip-match-card--own\" : \"\"}`}>\n    24→      <div className=\"coinflip-match-card__creator\">\n    25→        <PlayerAvatar address={match.player1} size=\"sm\" enableMiniProfile={false} />\n    26→        <div className=\"coinflip-match-card__info\">\n    27→          <span className=\"coinflip-match-card__address\">\n    28→            {getDisplayName(match.player1)}\n    29→          </span>\n    30→          <span className=\"coinflip-match-card__time\">{timeAgo}</span>\n    31→        </div>\n    32→      </div>\n    33→\n    34→      <div className=\"coinflip-match-card__bet\">\n    35→        <div\n    36→          className={`coinflip-match-card__side coinflip-match-card__side--${match.player1Side}`}\n    37→        >\n    38→          <span className=\"coinflip-match-card__rng\">RNG</span>\n    39→        </div>\n    40→        <div className=\"coinflip-match-card__amount\">\n    41→          {match.entryAmount} SOL\n    42→        </div>\n    43→        <div\n    44→          className=\"coinflip-match-card__tier\"\n    45→          style={{\n    46→            color: TIER_COLORS[match.tier],\n    47→            textShadow: `0 0 8px ${TIER_COLORS[match.tier]}`\n    48→          }}\n    49→        >\n    50→          {match.tier}\n    51→        </div>\n    52→      </div>\n    53→\n    54→      <div className=\"coinflip-match-card__actions\">\n    55→        {!isOwn && onJoin && (\n    56→          <button\n    57→            type=\"button\"\n    58→            className=\"coinflip-match-card__join-btn\"\n    59→            onClick={onJoin}\n    60→            disabled={!canJoin || joining}\n    61→          >\n    62→            {joining ? \"Joining...\" : \"Join\"}\n    63→          </button>\n    64→        )}\n    65→        {isOwn && (\n    66→          <span className=\"coinflip-match-card__status\">Waiting...</span>\n    67→        )}\n    68→      </div>\n    69→    </div>\n    70→  );\n    71→}\n    72→\n    73→function getTimeAgo(timestamp: number): string {\n    74→  const seconds = Math.floor((Date.now() - timestamp) / 1000);\n    75→\n    76→  if (seconds < 60) return `${seconds}s ago`;\n    77→  if (seconds < 3600) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 60)}m ago`;\n    78→  if (seconds < 86400) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 3600)}h ago`;\n    79→  return `${Math.floor(seconds / 86400)}d ago`;\n    80→}\n    81→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Qc7P4PDwDUdRywkRf8KCN9","session_id":"44b168fb-5e34-4073-98cb-22d0c5867ea1","uuid":"6359bf66-c049-419b-b63f-c021635c0da1"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Qc7P4PDwDUdRywkRf8KCN9","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have a complete picture. Let me create a summary report of what I found.\n\n## Summary: Coinflip Page Component Architecture\n\nI've located and reviewed all the key files for the Coinflip page component. Here's the complete wiring:\n\n### Main Entry Point: CoinflipPage\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipPage.tsx`\n\nThe `CoinflipPage` component wraps `CoinflipPageContent` with the `CoinflipProvider`:\n\n```typescript\nexport function CoinflipPage() {\n  return (\n    <CoinflipProvider>\n      <CoinflipPageContent />\n    </CoinflipProvider>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Core Context: CoinflipContext\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx`\n\nThis context manages all match state and actions:\n\n- **State:**\n  - `activeMatch: UIMatch | null` — the current match the user is in\n  - `openMatches: UIMatch[]` — all available matches in the lobby\n  - `userHistory: UIMatch[]` — past matches\n  - `selectedTier: Tier | null` — tier selection for creating a match\n  - `selectedSide: CoinSide | null` — heads/tails selection\n\n- **Actions:**\n  - `createMatch()` — creates a new match with selected tier/side\n  - `joinMatch(matchId)` — joins an existing match from the lobby\n  - `cancelMatch()` — cancels the active match\n  - `claimPayout()` — claims winnings\n  - `clearActiveMatch()` — returns to lobby\n  - `refreshMatches()` — polls for open matches every 5 seconds\n\n- **Polling:** Automatically refreshes open matches every 5 seconds via `setInterval`, and polls the active match if one exists.\n\n### Page Content Structure\n\n`CoinflipPageContent` uses `useCoinflip()` to access context and renders:\n\n1. **Sidebar** (left panel):\n   - Tier selector (`TierSelector`)\n   - Coin side selector (`CoinSideSelector`)\n   - Summary display (entry amount, potential payout)\n   - Action button (Create Game or shows current game info when `activeMatch` exists)\n\n2. **Main Content** (right panel):\n   - Either `ActiveMatchView` if `activeMatch` exists (shows the active game)\n   - Or `OpenMatchesList` if no active match (shows lobby with all open games)\n\n3. **History Modal:**\n   - Displays past match details when user clicks on history entry\n\n### OpenMatchesList Component\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx`\n\nRenders the lobby browser with:\n- **Props:**\n  - `matches: UIMatch[]` — from context's `openMatches`\n  - `loading: boolean` — from context's `loading` state\n  - `onJoin: (matchId: string) => void` — calls context's `joinMatch()`\n  - `joiningMatchId: string | null` — tracks which match is being joined\n  - `currentUserAddress: string | null` — to identify own matches\n  - `selectedTier: Tier | null` — filters displayed matches by tier\n  - `isConnected: boolean` — enables/disables join button\n\n- **Filtering:** If `selectedTier` is set, shows only matches with that tier\n- **States:** Loading spinner, empty state message, or list of `MatchCard` components\n\n### MatchCard Component\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx`\n\nEach match in the lobby renders as a card showing:\n- Creator info (avatar, address, time ago)\n- Bet details (side chosen, amount in SOL, tier with colored styling)\n- Join button (disabled if match is owned by current user or user is not connected)\n\n### Components Barrel Export\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/index.ts`\n\n```typescript\nexport { CoinSideSelector } from \"./CoinSideSelector\";\nexport { CoinAnimation } from \"./CoinAnimation\";\nexport { MatchCard } from \"./MatchCard\";\nexport { OpenMatchesList } from \"./OpenMatchesList\";\nexport { ActiveMatchView } from \"./ActiveMatchView\";\n```\n\n### Data Flow Summary\n\n1. **Page Load:** `CoinflipProvider` initializes, context fetches all open matches via `fetchAllOpenMatches()`\n2. **Polling:** Every 5 seconds, open matches refresh automatically\n3. **User Creates Match:** Calls `createMatch()` → builds transaction → sets `activeMatch`\n4. **User Joins Match:** Clicks \"Join\" on a `MatchCard` → calls `joinMatch(matchId)` → sets `activeMatch`\n5. **Back to Lobby:** Calls `clearActiveMatch()` → shows `OpenMatchesList` again\n6. **Match Completes:** Polling detects completion → updates `activeMatch` state\n\nAll state is centralized in `CoinflipContext`, allowing components to subscribe to changes and re-render automatically as the match state evolves."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: acf23b8 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 33400\ntool_uses: 9\nduration_ms: 37679</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"44b168fb-5e34-4073-98cb-22d0c5867ea1","uuid":"a15e64a6-5edf-4665-b15b-678552bae813","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Search for the main Coinflip page component that renders the lobby browser. Look for files like CoinflipPage.tsx, CoinflipGamePage.tsx, or similar in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`. Also look for any component that uses OpenMatchesList and CoinflipContext together to understand how they're wired. Also check the components barrel file at `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/index.ts`. Return the full contents of relevant files.","agentId":"acf23b8","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have a complete picture. Let me create a summary report of what I found.\n\n## Summary: Coinflip Page Component Architecture\n\nI've located and reviewed all the key files for the Coinflip page component. Here's the complete wiring:\n\n### Main Entry Point: CoinflipPage\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipPage.tsx`\n\nThe `CoinflipPage` component wraps `CoinflipPageContent` with the `CoinflipProvider`:\n\n```typescript\nexport function CoinflipPage() {\n  return (\n    <CoinflipProvider>\n      <CoinflipPageContent />\n    </CoinflipProvider>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Core Context: CoinflipContext\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx`\n\nThis context manages all match state and actions:\n\n- **State:**\n  - `activeMatch: UIMatch | null` — the current match the user is in\n  - `openMatches: UIMatch[]` — all available matches in the lobby\n  - `userHistory: UIMatch[]` — past matches\n  - `selectedTier: Tier | null` — tier selection for creating a match\n  - `selectedSide: CoinSide | null` — heads/tails selection\n\n- **Actions:**\n  - `createMatch()` — creates a new match with selected tier/side\n  - `joinMatch(matchId)` — joins an existing match from the lobby\n  - `cancelMatch()` — cancels the active match\n  - `claimPayout()` — claims winnings\n  - `clearActiveMatch()` — returns to lobby\n  - `refreshMatches()` — polls for open matches every 5 seconds\n\n- **Polling:** Automatically refreshes open matches every 5 seconds via `setInterval`, and polls the active match if one exists.\n\n### Page Content Structure\n\n`CoinflipPageContent` uses `useCoinflip()` to access context and renders:\n\n1. **Sidebar** (left panel):\n   - Tier selector (`TierSelector`)\n   - Coin side selector (`CoinSideSelector`)\n   - Summary display (entry amount, potential payout)\n   - Action button (Create Game or shows current game info when `activeMatch` exists)\n\n2. **Main Content** (right panel):\n   - Either `ActiveMatchView` if `activeMatch` exists (shows the active game)\n   - Or `OpenMatchesList` if no active match (shows lobby with all open games)\n\n3. **History Modal:**\n   - Displays past match details when user clicks on history entry\n\n### OpenMatchesList Component\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx`\n\nRenders the lobby browser with:\n- **Props:**\n  - `matches: UIMatch[]` — from context's `openMatches`\n  - `loading: boolean` — from context's `loading` state\n  - `onJoin: (matchId: string) => void` — calls context's `joinMatch()`\n  - `joiningMatchId: string | null` — tracks which match is being joined\n  - `currentUserAddress: string | null` — to identify own matches\n  - `selectedTier: Tier | null` — filters displayed matches by tier\n  - `isConnected: boolean` — enables/disables join button\n\n- **Filtering:** If `selectedTier` is set, shows only matches with that tier\n- **States:** Loading spinner, empty state message, or list of `MatchCard` components\n\n### MatchCard Component\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx`\n\nEach match in the lobby renders as a card showing:\n- Creator info (avatar, address, time ago)\n- Bet details (side chosen, amount in SOL, tier with colored styling)\n- Join button (disabled if match is owned by current user or user is not connected)\n\n### Components Barrel Export\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/index.ts`\n\n```typescript\nexport { CoinSideSelector } from \"./CoinSideSelector\";\nexport { CoinAnimation } from \"./CoinAnimation\";\nexport { MatchCard } from \"./MatchCard\";\nexport { OpenMatchesList } from \"./OpenMatchesList\";\nexport { ActiveMatchView } from \"./ActiveMatchView\";\n```\n\n### Data Flow Summary\n\n1. **Page Load:** `CoinflipProvider` initializes, context fetches all open matches via `fetchAllOpenMatches()`\n2. **Polling:** Every 5 seconds, open matches refresh automatically\n3. **User Creates Match:** Calls `createMatch()` → builds transaction → sets `activeMatch`\n4. **User Joins Match:** Clicks \"Join\" on a `MatchCard` → calls `joinMatch(matchId)` → sets `activeMatch`\n5. **Back to Lobby:** Calls `clearActiveMatch()` → shows `OpenMatchesList` again\n6. **Match Completes:** Polling detects completion → updates `activeMatch` state\n\nAll state is centralized in `CoinflipContext`, allowing components to subscribe to changes and re-render automatically as the match state evolves."}],"totalDurationMs":37679,"totalTokens":33400,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1192,"cache_read_input_tokens":30876,"output_tokens":1330,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1192,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
